commit.message:
Merge pull request #2 from Maxinoume/master

Fixed sass file class selector indentation
Fixed sass file class selector indentation

Merge pull request #1 from kserin/fix-nodesass-compilation

Fix sass compilation with node sass
Fix sass compilation with node sass

Contract & Tests initiated.

-Contract created
-Test suite written
-Deployment script written
-README.md written

Google login and improved error handling

Implemented Google authentication in user.auth.js
Added more specific error messages for login and signup processes
Updated User model to accommodate Google-authenticated users
Modified existing login and signup routes to handle new error cases

API Documentation:

Updated swagger.yaml to include new Google authentication endpoint
Added more specific error responses to existing endpoints
Improved description of request/response structures

Security enhancements:

Improved password handling for non-Google users
Added checks to prevent conflicts between Google and non-Google accounts

Code quality improvements:

Refactored Login component for better readability and maintainability
Improved error handling throughout the authentication flow
Fix on documentation & added package description.

Implement unit testing and Swagger documentation

- Add Jest and Supertest for comprehensive unit testing
  - Create test suite for user routes (auth, CRUD operations)
  - Mock authentication and authorization middleware
  - Test admin and moderator level access control

- Integrate Swagger for API documentation
  - Set up Swagger UI for interactive API exploration
  - Configure Swagger in app.js with OpenAPI 3.1.0 specification
  - Document API endpoints using JSDoc comments in route files

- Update project structure and dependencies
  - Organize files into appropriate directories (auth, config, controller, etc.)
  - Use Yarn as the package manager
  - Update README.md with accurate project information and setup instructions

- Enhance error handling and input validation in user controller

- Implement role-based access control (User, Moderator, Admin)

Merge pull request #1 from alakise/alakise-patch-1

Update README.md
